pageProduct.name: U by Kotex Ultra Thin Overnight Long Wing 8 Pack
pageProduct.description:
General Information

U by Kotex Overnight Long Ultra Thin Pads give you that extra level of protection while you sleep. U by Kotex® Overnight Long pads are even longer and wider than Overnight Regular pads, for ultimate overnight protection.

  • Rapid-dry core Draws moisture away for faster absorption
  • Grooves that channel the moisture into the centre of the pad
  • Secure wings Keep the pad firmly in place
  • Unique 3 layer design For maximum absorbency
  • Anti-leak side guards At the side and the back

Size: 8 Pads
